1
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:37,410
[Return of the Queen]

2
00:01:38,289 --> 00:01:40,520
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:44,259
Since you've come to me in person
and made your request,

4
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:46,590
you must have thought everything through.

5
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,150
Go ahead.

6
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,920
What do you want?

7
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:52,640
Give Lu Siyu back to me.

8
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,039
You came here in person

9
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,229
and made your request.

10
00:01:59,229 --> 00:02:00,350
I thought

11
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,480
it would be

12
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,010
a truly imaginative offer.

13
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,690
I never expected

14
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,790
it would be my son.

15
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:16,630
It's Lu Siyu.

16
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,640
What's the difference?

17
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,400
Lu Sinan and Lu Siyu

18
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,079
are both my sons.

19
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:24,560
Of course there's

20
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,090
a difference between them.

21
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:28,079
But instead of worrying about that,

22
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,000
why don't you listen to

23
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,150
my conditions?

24
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,590
Conditions?

25
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,630
Go ahead.

26
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,310
Four years ago,

27
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,120
a business manager from Changlu Group

28
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,120
recommended to my father

29
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,840
a piece of land in West Asia,

30
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,560
claiming the 2 companies could invest

31
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,800
and develop it together.

32
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,800
But my father

33
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,630
had no plans

34
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:48,030
to expand into West Asia,

35
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,630
so he rejected the proposal.

36
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,750
Yet this proposal

37
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,190
was brought up 3 times

38
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:55,450
at Mare Nubium's board voting meetings,

39
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,590
enough to show

40
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,520
the eagerness and persistence

41
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,000
of the joint investor.

42
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,710
Later, that land was sold,

43
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:03,840
and for 4 whole years it sat abandoned,

44
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,830
undeveloped to this day.

45
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:06,840
And then?

46
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,800
I bought that land.

47
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,080
You bought that land?

48
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,470
As the president of Mare Nubium,

49
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,400
I am willing to use this land
as a starting point

50
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,630
to restart

51
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:22,090
the collaboration plan with Changlu Group.

52
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,870
How much of Mare Nubium's capital

53
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,000
did you use

54
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,930
to buy that land?

55
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,910
That's not your concern.

56
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,150
But

57
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,800
if Changlu wants this land,

58
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,140
I have conditions.

59
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,560
Name them.

60
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,620
I want the Lu family

61
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,680
to immediately announce to the public

62
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,910
that Lu Sinan's notarized will is invalid.

63
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:46,240
The Lu family and its insiders

64
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,030
must withdraw from Mare Nubium's board

65
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,310
and no longer be involved

66
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:51,310
in any of Mare Nubium's business affairs.

67
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:51,960
Also,

68
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,850
I'll take Siyu with me.

69
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,750
What's so funny?

70
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,520
I really underestimated you.

71
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,280
Thirty years ago,

72
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,030
your father and I

73
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,400
met through business.

74
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,030
You could say

75
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:14,430
I watched you grow up since you were born.

76
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,360
In my eyes,

77
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,950
you've always been

78
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,680
a little girl who always needed

79
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,480
her father's close protection.

80
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,240
But now,

81
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:24,170
you're sitting in front of me,

82
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,240
openly negotiating terms

83
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,430
with me.

84
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,040
A negotiation is a negotiation.

85
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,560
Age is irrelevant.

86
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,170
Do you even have the qualification

87
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,680
to negotiate with me?

88
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,750
Don't think that just because you've sat

89
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,310
in the president's chair at Mare Nubium
for a few days,

90
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,310
you actually have

91
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:45,800
what it takes to hold it.

92
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,600
Can you maneuver capital?

93
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,800
Can you expand networks?

94
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,270
Can you even control

95
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:52,920
those veteran shareholders

96
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,310
of Mare Nubium?

97
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,720
In my eyes,

98
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,430
you're just

99
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,750
a fledgling

100
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,630
little girl.

101
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:00,830
You took over Mare Nubium,
such a massive enterprise,

102
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,040
from your father

103
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,240
right from the start.

104
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,240
Faced with such an empire,

105
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:06,950
can you protect it?

106
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:09,400
Can you even hold your seat?

107
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,240
Are you discriminating against me?

108
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,720
Discrimination?

109
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,300
The business world is a battlefield.

110
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,160
It's not something you can handle

111
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,360
just by lifting a finger.

112
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:22,090
You want to sit at the card table
with Mare Nubium,

113
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,630
but anyone at that table

114
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:25,600
can knock you flat on your back.

115
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:32,080
Sit at the card table with Mare Nubium?

116
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:33,920
What card?

117
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,430
What table?

118
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,000
Who's sitting at this table?

119
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,680
And what do they have to knock me down?

120
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,430
When your father was alive,

121
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:46,230
did he never teach you anything?

122
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,190
You and my father had years of friendship.

123
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:52,720
Why don't you teach me?

124
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,190
Fine.

125
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:58,040
Then I'll make it clear for you.

126
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,560
Don't think that just because you found

127
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,360
that piece of land Changlu Group

128
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,870
had its eye on 4 years ago,

129
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:06,480
you can use it as a bargaining chip.

130
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,070
Ye Haimeng,

131
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,510
stop joking.

132
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,270
Changlu Group

133
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,600
doesn't need that land.

134
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:14,830
So there's absolutely no need

135
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:16,240
to collaborate

136
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,240
with Mare Nubium.

137
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,400
You don't want that land?

138
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,950
Then what do you want?

139
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,390
Your Mare Nubium.

140
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,270
After you married Sinan,

141
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,630
you should have been obedient

142
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:39,870
as his wife

143
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,960
and
the Lu family's eldest daughter-in-law,

144
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,240
and handed over everything
you couldn't protect

145
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,750
to the Lu family.

146
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:49,270
Then the Lu family could have ensured you

147
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:51,530
a safe, worry-free, and prosperous life

148
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:53,030
for the rest of your days.

149
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:56,690
Lu Sinan deliberately approached me

150
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,780
and tricked me into marrying him.

151
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:01,020
Was that planned by the Lu family?

152
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,010
What did you think?

153
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,390
Lu Sinan tried to kill me.

154
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,400
That was also on your orders?

155
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,750
Yes.

156
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,160
So what?

157
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:19,600
What?

158
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,870
Surprised?

159
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:22,720
Lu Sinan was

160
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,450
the eldest son of the Lu family.

161
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,000
Getting married and having children
were important matters to him.

162
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,190
As his father,

163
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:30,430
of course I would personally oversee it.

164
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:33,040
And you were the best candidate

165
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,510
I specially picked

166
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,630
for Lu Sinan.

167
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,750
Best?

168
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,040
You mean the best candidate to be killed.
Right?

169
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,000
You don't need to trick me into talking.

170
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,390
And you don't need to tell me

171
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,390
you hate Sinan and the Lu family now.

172
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,360
Actually, the ones you should hate most

173
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,870
are your own parents.

174
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,430
Why did they

175
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:55,040
only have one daughter?

176
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,310
Why did your father insist on handing over

177
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,510
Mare Nubium, such a massive enterprise,

178
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,040
to a daughter?

179
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,010
What ability do you have

180
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,920
to manage

181
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,950
such an empire?

182
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,920
What ability do you have

183
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,270
to protect the entire Mare Nubium?

184
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,720
Ye Haimeng,

185
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,850
you can't protect Mare Nubium.

186
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,570
So why not hand it over?

187
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,000
Merge it with Changlu Capital,

188
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,510
and let me and the Lu family
protect it for you.

189
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,600
That way,

190
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,750
the Lu family can still ensure

191
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:23,480
you live safely and worry-freely
for the rest of your life.

192
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,630
Even if the Lu family
doesn't take you down,

193
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,040
other families

194
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,950
will tear your Mare Nubium

195
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,160
to pieces until nothing remains.

196
00:08:32,789 --> 00:08:35,120
Mare Nubium is my family's business.

197
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,630
Why should it be merged into your Changlu?

198
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:38,549
How dare you

199
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:41,000
talk about murder and seizing wealth

200
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,440
as if it were

201
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,270
as simple as eating and drinking?

202
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:45,270
What right do you have to decide my fate

203
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:46,670
and my family's destiny?

204
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,510
In the world of capital,

205
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,030
there aren't so many whys.

206
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,720
The strong prey on the weak.

207
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,900
That's the natural order.

208
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:57,970
You're weak,

209
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:01,390
so you must die.

210
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,720
Open the door!

211
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,870
Is anybody here?

212
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,150
Siyu.

213
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:18,950
What's wrong?

214
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,870
Open the door!

215
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:21,840
Siyu!

216
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:22,960
Siyu!

217
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,160
Be careful with your wound.

218
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:26,960
I'll open it for you.

219
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,090
I'll open it for you.

220
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,000
Is your hand okay?

221
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:32,600
Siyu.

222
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:34,550
Siyu!

223
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,840
Lu Siyu, what's wrong with you?

224
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,970
Why did you push your brother-in-law?

225
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,370
Are you okay, Honey?

226
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,150
I'm fine.

227
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,610
Are you hurt from the fall?

228
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,050
Are you alright?

229
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,390
That brat.

230
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:52,480
Stop coming to negotiate with me

231
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,280
and trying to be clever about it.

232
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:55,850
You don't have the ability

233
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,530
or the qualification.

234
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,930
Joint overseas land development?

235
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,390
My Changlu Group

236
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,600
doesn't need it.

237
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,880
I've already given you the life

238
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,780
of the Lu family's eldest son.

239
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,680
Now the only thing the Lu family wants is

240
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:13,550
your Mare Nubium.

241
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:15,870
If you're smart enough,

242
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,030
you should obediently step down

243
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,560
as Mare Nubium's president

244
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,080
and hand over all the shares

245
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,980
jointly held by you and Sinan,

246
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,440
as well as those you took

247
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,670
from your Uncle Yuezhi,

248
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:27,150
to the Lu family.

249
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:28,630
That way,

250
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:30,120
the Lu family can still ensure

251
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:33,380
you live safely and worry-freely
for the rest of your life.

252
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,750
As for Siyu,

253
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,960
I'll have him take your place

254
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,910
as the largest controlling board director

255
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,510
of Mare Nubium.

256
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,080
Ye Haimeng,

257
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,200
just abandon any thought

258
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,510
of taking him away!

259
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,390
No way!

260
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,930
I will never be manipulated by you.

261
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,750
I will never go to Mare Nubium.

262
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,910
I won't harm Ye Haimeng.

263
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,550
And I will never,

264
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:02,080
like my brother,

265
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,910
take away all her assets.

266
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,720
Lu Siyu.

267
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:07,790
I won't become

268
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:09,270
the knife that hurts her!

269
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,400
Not unless I'm dead!

270
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,170
Come with me.

271
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:20,750
Lu Siyu!

272
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,270
Come back here!

273
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:41,920
It's okay.

274
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,890
They didn't follow us here.

275
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,680
Don't be afraid.

276
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:52,480
I won't let them hurt you.

277
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,390
You were slapped?

278
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:08,710
It's nothing.

279
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,650
It doesn't hurt.

280
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,200
Such serious injury—

281
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,720
how could it not hurt?

282
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:18,090
As long as you're not hurt,

283
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:19,590
I don't feel any pain.

284
00:12:30,510 --> 00:12:31,240
I'm sorry.

285
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,680
None of this has anything to do with you.

286
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,550
They are my family.

287
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,390
He's my father.

288
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,360
They've repeatedly

289
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,080
hurt you.

290
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,370
How could it have nothing to do with me?

291
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,360
You said

